reviewText:
I like the female fight action movies (woman or women defeat man or men). But in this movie, female action scene was less than I had expected. PRODUCER AND SUPERVISOR MUST WATCH THE FOLLOWING MOVIES if they produce the female action movies.

(1)Xena Warrior Princess series

(2)Tomb Raider

(3)Ultraviolet

(4)Sister Dragon (Japanese title: Onna Hissatsu Ken)
